    "original_title": "Golaha Wasiirada XFS oo kala diray maamulkii Rugta Ganacsiga Soomaaliyeed.",
    "slug": "somalia-s-cabinet-dissolves-chamber-of-commerce-board-appoints-interim-leader",
    "summary": "The Somali federal cabinet has approved the dissolution of the Somali Chamber of Commerce board and named Yasin Mahamud Ibar as interim chairman to lead election preparations.",
    "content": "The Council of Ministers of the Federal Republic of Somalia, during its regular meeting chaired by Prime Minister Hamza Abdi Barre, approved a proposal from the Ministry of Commerce and Industry to dissolve the previous board of the Somali Chamber of Commerce. The decision, reached on July 16, 2026, resulted in the appointment of Yasin Mahamud Ibar as the interim chairman of the chamber.\n\nAccording to the cabinet’s directive, Ibar will be responsible for organizing the electoral process and establishing a new board within a two-month period. This move aims to restructure the chamber, which serves as a key institution for facilitating trade and business representation in Somalia.\n\nThe dissolution follows a period of internal disputes and governance challenges within the chamber, which had hindered its ability to effectively advocate for the private sector. The government’s intervention is seen as an effort to restore confidence and ensure transparent leadership elections.\n\nFor the Somali diaspora, the chamber’s restructuring holds particular significance as it plays a vital role in connecting diaspora investors with local business opportunities. A stable and credible chamber can enhance investment flows from Somalis abroad, who are key contributors to the country’s economic development.\n\nThe interim chairman is expected to work closely with the Ministry of Commerce and Industry to ensure a smooth transition and fair elections. The cabinet’s approval underscores the government’s focus on reforming economic institutions to support growth and accountability.\n\nRead the original report from Goobjoog here: https://goobjoog.com/2026/07/16/golaha-wasiirada-xfs-oo-kala-diray-maamulkii-rugta-ganacsiga-soomaaliyeed/",
